message.body: Haha. Gorilla man is going to be in pitch perfect 2!

I started out doing realllllly well. I knew all the answers........and then it just plummeted! Seriously. It's those damn crosses...we had to write them out and it was horrible! Plus...I had no idea how to diagram how a calico cat could be male!

I know. It was those damned crosses. Eff those crosses. It was weird though. Cause he was like you have a white flower and red flower. Use a punnet square to show how it's incomplete dominance. I didn't have any examples so I totallllly guessed. Argh! And figures everyone around me is like "Ohhh! it wasn't bad at all!"
It's the worst when everyone's like "it wasn't bad" and then when everyone struggled and you're the only who thinks it wasn't bad you freak out too.

So I was so mad last night. I put emmy in her crate around 11:40 and she barked until like 12:10. Damn half an hr of a low barking noise. The entire time I was trying to sleep and I was getting annoyed. So i finally said "emmy! Stop!" And she did, just like that. I was so mad cause if I had just said that after 5 mins, she probably would've stopped.
